Name: adenosarcoma
Definition: A carcinosarcoma that derives_from simultaneously or consecutively in mesodermal tissue and glandular epithelium.

Name: adenomyoma
Definition: A carcinosarcoma that has_material_basis_in gland and muscle components.

Name: malignant adenofibroma
Definition: A cervical cancer that has_material_basis_in abnormally proliferating cells derives_from melanocytes.
